Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.83,0:00:14.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,敵人有幾台?還剩幾台?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.56,0:00:17.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小林機嚴重損壞 山本機失去聯絡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.72,0:00:20.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.66,0:00:21.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.91,0:00:49.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幽{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.20,0:00:51.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幽靈{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.57,0:02:45.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,精英偵察隊全滅啊{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.67,0:02:49.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,彈夾空了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.22,0:02:52.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打光了最後一發子彈
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.19,0:02:55.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這都是第幾次了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.79,0:02:57.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還全是久經沙場的老兵
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.98,0:03:04.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,學長 你怎麼看
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.44,0:03:06.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.29,0:03:11.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,彷彿是驚恐至極四處逃命時{\rsymbol}…{\r}被全殲的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.48,0:03:13.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.66,0:03:16.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,究竟{\rsymbol}…{\r}遭到了什麼攻擊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.03,0:03:20.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從殘骸上看 應該是曳戰者
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.19,0:03:22.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會是敵人的新型機嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.19,0:03:24.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.58,0:03:29.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是{\rsymbol}…{\r}青藍和銀色殲滅者 終有一天也會變成舊型
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.21,0:03:34.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,兵器{\rsymbol}…{\r}完成設計開發 投入實戰之時
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.30,0:03:37.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不就已經過時了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.57,0:03:41.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.01,0:03:45.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,隊長 莫非真的{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.51,0:03:47.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幽靈嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.55,0:03:59.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好 好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.75,0:04:01.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,保持繼續 慢慢來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.99,0:04:08.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奧爾貝 希莫西亞 西坐摩原 肯尼文 以及北坐摩原
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.68,0:04:11.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,敵人在這些附近重覆攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.47,0:04:15.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幽靈{\rsymbol}…{\r}嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.77,0:04:19.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鈴城曹長 在士兵面前請別用這個稱呼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.26,0:04:22.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝 我會注意的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.76,0:04:27.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,敵人攻擊的共通點 全都是殲滅戰
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.23,0:04:30.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所有現場 都沒有倖存者
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.30,0:04:34.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是不想留下目擊情報嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.79,0:04:36.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很有可能
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.98,0:04:41.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為應對這不明身份的敵人 我軍鋪開了複數部隊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.36,0:04:47.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不論怎樣 你們獨立第八部隊 既然被派到這北坐摩原
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.67,0:04:52.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就表明作戰指揮部很清楚這駐地的重要性
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.40,0:04:59.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又或者 敵人為實戰測試新武器 選擇了偏僻地區
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.98,0:05:06.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,局部的戰術勝利 並不等於大局上戰略勝利
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.00,0:05:08.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼看這場戰爭
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.17,0:05:13.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,強的一方獲勝 差不多就這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.71,0:05:20.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,確實大尉{\rsymbol}…{\r}多少有點權威主義
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.82,0:05:22.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但不必說那種話吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.79,0:05:26.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,部隊執勤時間變更
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.53,0:05:29.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,立刻去辦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.00,0:05:38.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然說清楚比較好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.12,0:05:41.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不小心聽了他姐姐的事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.72,0:05:46.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誒 青藍還有這機能啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.79,0:05:48.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,時宗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.86,0:05:50.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 怎麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.86,0:05:53.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那{\rsymbol}…{\r}那啥{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.32,0:05:57.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剛才有郵件 傳來了銀色殲滅者控制插件的升級補丁
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.73,0:05:59.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,安{\rsymbol}…{\r}裝前記得檢查一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.98,0:06:01.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,呃{\rsymbol}…{\r}嗯{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.72,0:06:07.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.23,0:06:11.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這時候導入新型機嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.83,0:06:14.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,澤爾准將操持的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.36,0:06:15.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒法說不
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.90,0:06:21.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,機師的訓練 兵站的處理 現場的負擔都是問題啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.66,0:06:26.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要撬動膠著戰局 需要震撼療法
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.50,0:06:28.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,負責開發的福達格倫特公司
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.86,0:06:34.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,據說在各處塞了不少鈔票 強攬了這筆活
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.57,0:06:36.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不該說的別說
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.86,0:06:39.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咱們可被情報部盯著呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.70,0:06:40.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.78,0:06:43.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然不知澤爾打得什麼算盤
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.49,0:06:48.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,繞過情報部購入新型機 是想借我們個人情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.72,0:06:51.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就讓他這麼想吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.43,0:07:01.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可別忘了 卡普
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.91,0:07:07.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不論面對澤爾還是情報部 我們一定要裝成傻子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.59,0:07:08.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.59,0:07:10.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這全是為了祖國
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.10,0:07:26.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,覺得飯菜如何
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.03,0:07:28.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吃不如量足
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.98,0:07:32.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這種高檔餐廳的飯菜 可填不飽肚子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.23,0:07:39.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是因戈爾米亞的新型機
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.78,0:07:44.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我這人討厭繞彎子 你知道的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.56,0:07:45.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.01,0:07:47.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要我們追加下單?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.67,0:07:50.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,您明察 在下佩服
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.30,0:07:51.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.06,0:07:55.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也明白你的立場
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.34,0:07:58.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但這玩意用了柯貝爾尼斯的技術吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.76,0:08:03.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,偶然一致罷了 而且技術本無國界
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.83,0:08:05.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嘴還真硬
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.48,0:08:07.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那件事如何了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.19,0:08:09.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哪件?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.85,0:08:13.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\rsymbol2}「{\r}那件{\rsymbol2}」{\r}除了U-Link還能有什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.38,0:08:14.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別裝傻了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.68,0:08:18.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,絕無問題 請相信敝公司的技術
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.98,0:08:22.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在薩卡拉岬角那時也是這句話吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.64,0:08:26.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,薩卡拉岬角?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.23,0:08:34.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為應對敵人新型曳戰者攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.84,0:08:39.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即刻起 你們進入12小時兩班輪換的迎擊狀態
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.66,0:08:44.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今晚2000時起 至明早0800時
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.57,0:08:47.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由進上等兵和波特曼上等兵值崗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.74,0:08:50.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,指揮由先入隊的進上等兵擔當
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.85,0:08:51.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.83,0:08:56.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,0800時起 由阿普爾頓軍曹和朱利亞諾伍長值崗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.52,0:08:57.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.42,0:09:01.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,另外 哈茲福特小姐 作為銀色殲滅者運行輔助人員
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.51,0:09:04.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請協助一同值夜崗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.95,0:09:05.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.46,0:09:07.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有問題嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.96,0:09:10.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,隊長
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.28,0:09:15.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,作戰指揮部希望繳獲敵機 但敵人性能未知
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.23,0:09:19.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,視現場情況 允許當機立斷將其擊毀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.95,0:09:20.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.32,0:09:44.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.80,0:09:52.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,波特曼小姐呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.25,0:09:54.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,廚房
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.49,0:09:57.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剛才使勁求主廚 非要親手做晚飯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.04,0:09:59.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.31,0:10:01.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\rsymbol2}「{\r}誒{\rsymbol2}」{\r}什麼 啥意思
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.43,0:10:04.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒啥 就是有點意外
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.34,0:10:11.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,開暖氣了嗎 你不覺得冷?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.58,0:10:13.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,畢竟是沙漠
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.30,0:10:15.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,毯子啥的 應該隨手就能找到
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.08,0:10:26.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 那啥{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.83,0:10:27.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.92,0:10:30.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事? 插件我檢查過了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.52,0:10:31.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.65,0:10:35.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個啥 最近狀態挺好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.74,0:10:37.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你和銀色殲滅者
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.24,0:10:37.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.07,0:10:40.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聯動深度也一直在漲
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.89,0:10:44.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我這當負責人的 也覺得臉上有光呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.59,0:10:46.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你咋了 看著這麼彆扭
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.22,0:10:47.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,呃{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.65,0:10:53.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我{\rsymbol}…{\r}之前不小心聽到了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.02,0:10:53.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.53,0:10:57.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,時宗的{\rsymbol}…{\r}那個{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.62,0:10:59.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐和左文字隊長的事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.07,0:11:03.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是故意偷聽的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.66,0:11:06.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是碰巧聽見鈴城小姐說話
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.98,0:11:08.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的哦{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.52,0:11:09.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你聽了多少
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.05,0:11:16.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你姐姐和左文字隊長{\rsymbol}…{\r}那個{\rsymbol}…{\r}關係親密{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.33,0:11:21.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有 你姐姐去世時 他也在場
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.64,0:11:23.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全聽了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.56,0:11:25.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.35,0:11:29.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難怪最近 吉米都怪怪的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.66,0:11:33.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為那是隱私嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.54,0:11:35.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,裝不知道不就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.39,0:11:37.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我做不到啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.33,0:11:40.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 不用在意
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.56,0:11:41.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誒?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.45,0:11:44.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐因何而死
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.52,0:11:48.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,軍方咬定是事故 其他隻字不提
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.19,0:11:53.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是 聽鈴城小姐講完 終於知道了經過
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.69,0:11:55.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以沒事了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.87,0:11:58.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的沒事了?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.83,0:12:00.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你這麼一說又覺得有事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.83,0:12:01.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.76,0:12:02.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過 還是算了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.99,0:12:04.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到底怎樣啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.42,0:12:08.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知該怎麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.68,0:12:13.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我再怎麼糾結 過去的也回不來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.13,0:12:19.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,晚飯做好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.97,0:12:27.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那事兒都過了一週了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.99,0:12:30.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幽靈{\rsymbol}…{\r}不出現啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.41,0:12:32.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒準已經成佛了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.90,0:12:35.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 那可太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.23,0:12:37.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那怎麼可能啊 淨說傻話
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.20,0:12:41.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是這麼好對付 咱也不用費這勁
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.67,0:12:42.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,行了 走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.57,0:12:45.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不就開個玩笑嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.23,0:13:15.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saber-1呼叫Iron head
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.89,0:13:17.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,目前 正與敵人交戰
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.67,0:13:18.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請求火速支援
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.93,0:13:20.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Iron head 請回話
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.74,0:13:23.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saber-1 與因戈爾米亞的曳戰者交戰中
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.48,0:13:30.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saber-1 這裡是Iron head
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.43,0:13:31.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請回話 Saber-1
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.19,0:14:08.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全軍 進入位置
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.48,0:14:10.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,通電左文字中尉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.26,0:14:12.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,左文字中尉 接通
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.66,0:14:14.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.92,0:14:18.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,中尉 你手下的新型機 怎麼樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.55,0:14:19.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,準備好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.25,0:14:23.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,派到前面去 逐一告知狀況
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.93,0:14:24.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.59,0:14:39.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,敵人消滅了巡視中的巡邏隊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.15,0:14:42.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從方位一二五向總駐地移動中
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.51,0:14:43.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.02,0:14:47.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希爾菲 勞倫斯的青藍 已做好出擊準備
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.98,0:14:54.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,青藍-1 青藍-2 將與銀色殲滅者和青藍-3匯合
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.81,0:14:55.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.61,0:15:13.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,居然徑直衝這邊來了?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.78,0:15:15.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,前線怎麼樣了 抓緊應對
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.88,0:15:16.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.44,0:15:18.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不耍小伎倆嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.03,0:15:20.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,兩位 要小心
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.60,0:15:21.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.47,0:15:24.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,移動速度與銀色殲滅者相當 甚至更高
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.19,0:15:28.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,重新預計算接敵地點 發給機師
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.51,0:15:29.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.51,0:15:31.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,甘木大尉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.58,0:15:32.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.50,0:15:35.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,該把前線部隊再鋪開一些
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.02,0:15:37.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,指揮由我負責 你提供情報就行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.09,0:15:38.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.32,0:15:50.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,與以往的因戈爾米亞機速度不同
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.29,0:15:52.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,注意 它來了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.85,0:15:53.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.18,0:15:58.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上面
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.43,0:16:00.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誒?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.24,0:16:27.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個混賬{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.91,0:16:29.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奈美惠
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.64,0:16:31.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不要緊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.09,0:16:32.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奈美惠機 注意距離
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.82,0:16:33.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.88,0:16:36.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,甘木大尉 請散開基地內曳戰者
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.13,0:16:38.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.61,0:16:41.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希爾菲 勞倫斯 向後撤確保地形優勢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.51,0:16:42.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.25,0:16:42.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.47,0:16:51.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這就是新型機的威力?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.07,0:16:59.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.76,0:17:05.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希爾菲 勞倫斯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.07,0:17:06.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,時宗他們被突破了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.00,0:17:10.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是敵方炮擊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.76,0:17:44.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦喲 這可麻煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.77,0:17:45.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嘁
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.89,0:17:52.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.92,0:17:54.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打中啊 打中啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.84,0:17:55.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,學長
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.50,0:18:16.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.28,0:18:19.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聯動深度 70
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.84,0:18:20.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,75
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.26,0:18:22.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,80
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.51,0:18:33.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,報告狀況 集中火力攻擊敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.83,0:18:35.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,究竟在搞什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.20,0:18:42.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幽靈{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.17,0:18:53.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這混賬{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.67,0:19:25.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奈美惠
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.28,0:20:03.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,時宗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.16,0:20:23.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要緊吧 時宗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.63,0:20:25.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奈美惠 受傷沒?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.06,0:20:26.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有 我沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.55,0:20:46.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那部機體{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.61,0:20:51.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個問題怎麼樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.36,0:20:55.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,目前為止 沒有明顯徵兆
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.75,0:20:56.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.88,0:21:02.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,告訴柯貝爾尼斯和福達格倫特 計劃進入下一階段
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.82,0:21:09.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在NR綜合症顯露之前 要不惜一切完成量產
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.67,0:21:12.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這一點 命令兩公司嚴格遵守
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.05,0:21:21.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了 里希特霍芬少尉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.54,0:21:22.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,羅德里克少尉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.13,0:21:26.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,瞄準系統的延遲還沒有改善
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.91,0:21:28.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,需要立刻調整
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.01,0:21:32.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是整備班說 現階段這已經是極限了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.98,0:21:36.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,暴風-A必須常保完美狀態
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.37,0:21:38.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這就讓他們改善
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.80,0:21:46.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,關於下一個作戰目標{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.75,0:21:47.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,變更
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.04,0:21:48.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.23,0:21:51.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我找到它了——銀色殲滅者
